+\n| LINES                                      |                                |\n+--------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+\n| LOAD                                       |                                |\n+--------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+\n| LOCALTIME                                  |                                |\n+--------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+\n| LOCALTIMESTAMP                             |                                |\n+--------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+\n| LOCK                                       |                                |\n+--------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+\n| LONG                                       |                                |\n+--------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+\n| LONGBLOB                                   |                                |\n+--------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+\n| LONGTEXT                                   |                                |\n+--------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+\n| LOOP                                       |                                |\n+--------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+\n| LOW_PRIORITY                               |                                |\n+--------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+\n| MASTER_HEARTBEAT_PERIOD                    |                                |\n+--------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+\n| MASTER_SSL_VERIFY_SERVER_CERT              |                                |\n+--------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+\n| MATCH                                      |                                |\n+--------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+\n| MAXVALUE                                   |                                |\n+--------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+\n| MEDIUMBLOB                                 |                                |\n+--------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+\n| MEDIUMINT                                  |                                |\n+--------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+\n| MEDIUMTEXT                                 |                                |\n+--------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+\n| MIDDLEINT                                  |                                |\n+--------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+\n| MINUTE_MICROSECOND                         |                                |\n+--------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+\n| MINUTE_SECOND                              |                                |\n+--------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+\n| MOD                                        |                                |\n+--------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+\n| MODIFIES                                   |                                |\n+--------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+\n| NATURAL                                    |                                |\n+--------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+\n| NOT                                        |                                |\n+--------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+\n| NO_WRITE_TO_BINLOG                         |                                |\n+---------------------------